{
  "stem": "7093.6",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I see.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were at the -- [INAUDIBLE] we were at the-- 206 and 208.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One thing which I did not mention, which I forgot now to-- to put in and which is very, very important-- I mean, for me it's extremely important-- that before they put me to the appellplatz, these two women-- because they wanted to get rid of me-- they actually tried to bribe me.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The way they tried to bribe me, that they first-- after they found out that I knew German, they came to me and they offered me to become work leader.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- now, to become work leader would have been a wonderful thing because you had much more food, you had easier life.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It would have been wonderful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I refused it, because I said that I wanted to survive, but I did not want to survive any price.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, therefore, I said I am not prepared to push other people around, and I don't want to be work leader.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so I-- I refused it, and then the next day they came and put me into this [INAUDIBLE] for the selection, for these 206.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But once they saw that I was sent back, they didn't do anything about it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They left me in peace, and that was over with.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That saved me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Burying the dog or whatever saved my life because these 206 were sent back to Auschwitz and were never ever heard of again.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was the end of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They weren't sent to a paper factory, as they were told.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so this-- this was one story which was very important for me because I always felt I want to say that one did have a choice.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was a choice, at certain points.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
